<<< @/snippets/react/config.ts[config.ts]
:::

### message

`string | { raw: Hex | ByteArray } | undefined`

The message to be verified.

By default, wagmi verifies the UTF-8 representation of the message.

::: code-group
```tsx [index.tsx]
import { useVerifyMessage } from 'wagmi'

